TITLE: Event-driven quest
BRIEFING: This quest makes use of linked variables and event messaging

QRC:

MESSAGE: 1000
We're done!

QST:

variable _Counter_
variable @A

task _S.00_:
    when _Counter_ above 100
    say 1000
    finish

event _TestIncrementCounter_:
    pop @A
    setvar _Counter_ (_Counter_ + @A)
